## 🌐 Webhook Production Patterns
> Дата: 2026-05-01 | Источник: боевой опыт Анжелочки (ai-eggs/agent/tg_bot.py)

### Webhook vs Polling — углублённый выбор
```python
# Production: webhook с SSL + secret token
from aiogram.webhook.aiohttp_server import SimpleRequestHandler, setup_application
from aiohttp import web

WEBHOOK_PATH = f"/webhook/{BOT_TOKEN}"
WEBHOOK_URL = f"https://your-domain.ru{WEBHOOK_PATH}"

async def on_startup(bot: Bot):
    await bot.set_webhook(
        url=WEBHOOK_URL,
        secret_token=os.getenv("WEBHOOK_SECRET"),  # ОБЯЗАТЕЛЬНО!
        drop_pending_updates=True,
    )

# Fallback: polling с retry + backoff (как у Анжелочки)
max_retries = 5
for attempt in range(1, max_retries + 1):
    try:
        await bot.delete_webhook(drop_pending_updates=True)
        await dp.start_polling(bot, polling_timeout=30)
        break
    except Exception as e:
        if "conflict" in str(e).lower() or "409" in str(e).lower():
            wait = min(2 ** attempt, 30)
            await asyncio.sleep(wait)
            continue
        raise
```

